original: Dahlberg, Sven Oskar Eskil, kyrkoherde, Åby, f. 8/9/79 i Eskilstuna. G. 08 m. Anna Sjöberg. — Mog:ex. i Upps. 99, teol. fil. ex. 00, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov samt prästv. f. Linköp. stift 06. Past:adj. i Höreda o. Motala 06, i S :t Olai förs. i Norrköp. 07, v. pastor i Ö. Eneby 08, past:adj. där 09, kommin. i Kvildinge 16, kyr-koh. där sed. 22.
translated: Dahlberg, Sven Oskar Eskil, pastor, Åby, born September 8th, 1879 in Eskilstuna. Married in 1908 to Anna Sjöberg. Completed undergraduate studies in Uppsala in 1899 and received a degree in theology in 1900. Passed practical theological exams and was ordained in the Linköping diocese in 1906. Served as assistant pastor in Höreda and Motala in 1906 and in S:t Olai parish in Norrköping in 1907, as well as assistant pastor in Ö. Eneby in 1908 and assistant pastor there in 1909. Appointed chaplain in Kvildinge in 1916, and served as pastor there from 1922.
